A '''sand louse''' was a small insect known to inhabit arid environments, particularly deserts. They were generally regarded as pests as they would infest food and drinking water, spoiling them for consumption.<ref name="marvel66">[[Star Wars (1977) 66|''Star Wars'' (1977) 66]]</ref> They could be found on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]<ref name="marvel23" /> and [[Beheboth]].<ref name="marvel66" />

